Executive Summary

OSAC completed 7 key demos advancing production readiness. Highlights
include automated storage tenant onboarding with VAST integration (first
vendor-specific storage integration), Windows VM support, dedicated cluster
mode for workload isolation, and Keycloak organizations migration improving
auth scalability.

Developer experience improved significantly—new snapshot-based tooling
reduces environment setup from 45min to 20min and CI time from 2.5hr to 1hr.

